definitions.definition: The simplest nitroparaffin , CH 3 NO 2 ; a colourless oily liquid used in organic synthesis , and as a fuel for rockets , racing cars and model aircraft .

main_definition: ( organic chemistry ) The simplest nitroparaffin , CH 3 NO 2 ; a colourless oily liquid used in organic synthesis , and as a fuel for rockets , racing cars and model aircraft .
